<p class="MsoNormalM"><b>Day 1: Journey from Shimla to Kafnu</b></p>















<ul type="discd">
 <li>Stay:
     Comfortable homestay</li>
 <li>Travel
     Distance: ~208 km by road</li>
 <li>Travel
     Time: 8–9 hours approx.</li>
 <li>Starting
     Altitude: Shimla – 2,276 m / 7,467 ft</li>
 <li>Grade<b>:</b>
     Easy (road journey)</li>
</ul>















<p class="MsoNormalM">Your adventure begins with a scenic drive from Shimla,
winding through valleys and mountain roads that gradually reveal the beauty of
Himachal’s traditional wooden architecture. The road, though long and curvy,
offers glimpses of apple orchards and pine forests along the way. By the time
you arrive at the quiet village of Kafnu, evening will have set in. You’ll
settle into a cozy homestay where a warm dinner awaits, giving you the perfect
chance to rest and prepare for the trek ahead.<br />
<br />
</p>
















<p style="
line-height:normal"><span style="font-size:14.0pt">
<br />
</span></p>                           </div>
