<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Day 7: After Breakfast – Drive from Mudh to Kaza, Drop at Bus Stand</span></p>




<p>

After an early breakfast in Mudh Village, the drive from Mudh Village to  Kaza.</p>




<p>Enjoy the last views of the beautiful Pin Valley, with its stark mountains and peaceful villages.</p>




<p>The drive takes approximately 2–3 hours (about 50 km),

On arrival in Kaza, you'll be dropped at the Kaza Bus Stand, marking the official end of the Himalayan Hikers' service.&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you are Going to from Kaza to Manali, Shimla, or Reckong Peo Kaza available Taxi and Bus Service  

If staying back in Kaza, there are local guesthouses and cafes for a relaxed end to your trip.</p>                           </div>
